name: axios
text:
⌚️  WHEN TO EXPECT RESULTS:

Election officials in Georgia and North Carolina expressed confidence in being able to have clear (but not finalized) results on election night or the next day. https://t.co/dxeEdTpC4Q

name: axios
text:
Arizona, Florida and Texas declined to provide an estimated timeline for completed results due to elections looking different in each county and uncertainty about late-arriving mail-in ballots.

All three states have begun to count mail-in votes. https://t.co/dxeEdTpC4Q

name: axios
text:
In Michigan and Pennsylvania, we might not know the results until at least Friday.
https://t.co/dxeEdTpC4Q

text:
One vote in the 2020 election wasn’t cast from a voting booth or by mail, but from 250 miles up aboard the International Space Station.

However, NASA astronaut Kate Rubins is far from the first person to exercise her civic duty from orbit.

name: axios
text:
